---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="All 13 dental services under one roof in Huntington Beach. General, cosmetic, implants, Invisalign and more with Dr. Jason Fu."
  page="services"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="tag">/ Services</span>
    <h1>Every treatment,<br />one practice.</h1>
    <p>From routine checkups to dental implants and Invisalign® — all 13 services under one roof in Huntington Beach, led by Dr. Jason Fu.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book a consultation <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="cards reveal">
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">01 — General</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 2C6.5 2 5 4.5 5 7c0 2.5.8 4.8 1.6 7.5L8 22h8l1.4-7.5C18.2 11.8 19 9.5 19 7c0-2.5-1.5-5-4-5-1 0-1.8.5-3 .5-1.2 0-2-.5-3-.5z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>General Dentistry</h3><p>Cleanings, exams and gentle checkups — the backbone of a healthy smile.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 2C6.5 2 5 4.5 5 7c0 2.5.8 4.8 1.6 7.5L8 22h8l1.4-7.5C18.2 11.8 19 9.5 19 7c0-2.5-1.5-5-4-5-1 0-1.8.5-3 .5-1.2 0-2-.5-3-.5z"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">02 — Cosmetic</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 3C8 3 7 5 7 7c0 2 .6 3.8 1.2 6L9.5 19h5L16 13c.6-2.2 1.2-4 1.2-6 0-2-1-4-3.2-4-1 0-1.5.4-2 .4S11 3 10 3z"/><path d="M19 2l.5 1.5 1.5.5-1.5.5L19 6l-.5-1.5L17 4l1.5-.5z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Cosmetic Dentistry</h3><p>Whitening, veneers and bonding tailored to your goals for a brighter smile.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 3C8 3 7 5 7 7c0 2 .6 3.8 1.2 6L9.5 19h5L16 13c.6-2.2 1.2-4 1.2-6 0-2-1-4-3.2-4-1 0-1.5.4-2 .4S11 3 10 3z"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">03 — Restorative</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2v7"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="3" rx="1"/><path d="M10.5 12l-1 8h5l-1-8"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Dental Implants</h3><p>A permanent, natural-looking foundation for missing teeth, built to last.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2v7"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="3" rx="1"/><path d="M10.5 12l-1 8h5l-1-8"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">04 — Orthodontics</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 10c0-2.8 4-5 9-5s9 2.2 9 5v2a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><path d="M7 14v2.5M12 14.5V18M17 14v2.5"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Invisalign®</h3><p>Nearly-invisible aligners with a precise digital plan built around your life.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 10c0-2.8 4-5 9-5s9 2.2 9 5v2a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">05 — Restorative</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 20h18M5 20V10l3.5 4L12 3l3.5 11L19 10v10"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Crowns &amp; Bridges</h3><p>Custom restorations that blend seamlessly — many completed in a single visit.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 20h18M5 20V10l3.5 4L12 3l3.5 11L19 10v10"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">06 — Emergency</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9.5 2C7 2 5.5 4 5.5 6.5c0 2.3.7 4.3 1.4 7L8 20h8l1.1-6.5c.7-2.7 1.4-4.7 1.4-7C18.5 4 17 2 14.5 2z"/><path d="M13.5 7.5l-3 5H13l-2 4.5 5-7h-3z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Emergency Care</h3><p>Same-day appointments and fast, calm relief when you need it most.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9.5 2C7 2 5.5 4 5.5 6.5c0 2.3.7 4.3 1.4 7L8 20h8l1.1-6.5c.7-2.7 1.4-4.7 1.4-7C18.5 4 17 2 14.5 2z"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">07 — Cosmetic</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 3.5C8 3.5 7 5.5 7 7.5c0 2 .6 3.8 1.2 6L9.5 19h5L16 13.5c.6-2.2 1.2-4 1.2-6 0-2-1-4-3.2-4-1 0-1.5.5-2 .5S11 3.5 10 3.5z"/><path d="M19.5 3v2.5M18.2 4.3l1.8 1.8M20.5 4.8h-2.5"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Teeth Whitening</h3><p>In-office and take-home options — a brighter smile on your schedule.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M10 3.5C8 3.5 7 5.5 7 7.5c0 2 .6 3.8 1.2 6L9.5 19h5L16 13.5c.6-2.2 1.2-4 1.2-6 0-2-1-4-3.2-4-1 0-1.5.5-2 .5S11 3.5 10 3.5z"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">08 — Cosmetic</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="6" width="20" height="12" rx="2"/><path d="M8 6V4M16 6V4M2 10h20"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Veneers</h3><p>Thin, custom porcelain shells that transform the look of your front teeth.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="6" width="20" height="12" rx="2"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">09 — Restorative</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M9 12h6M12 9v6"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Root Canal</h3><p>Gentle, precise treatment to save an infected tooth and relieve pain fast.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">10 — General</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 6h18M3 12h18M3 18h18"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Extractions</h3><p>Gentle, stress-free removals with careful planning for your comfort and recovery.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 6h18M3 12h18M3 18h18"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">11 — Periodontal</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Periodontal Care</h3><p>Deep cleaning and gum therapy to protect the foundation of your smile.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">12 — Pediatric</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M6 20v-2a4 4 0 0 1 4-4h4a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v2"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Pediatric Dentistry</h3><p>Gentle, fun visits that build healthy habits and a love of the dentist early.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/></svg></div>
      </a>
      <a class="scell" href="/service">
        <div class="num">13 — Restorative</div>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Porcelain Bridges</h3><p>Replace one or more missing teeth with a natural-looking fixed restoration.</p>
        <span class="arr">Learn more →</span>
        <div class="bgico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/></svg></div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="ctacard reveal">
      <div class="grid-ov"></div>
      <div class="c"><span class="tag">New patients welcome</span><h2>Not sure where to start?</h2><p>Book a consultation and Dr. Fu will walk you through the best options for your smile — no pressure.</p></div>
      <div class="acts"><a class="btn" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a><a class="btn btn-o" href="/contact">Request a consult</a></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
